## What's happening?
ClickHouse on {{host.name}} has a high number of concurrently active queries over the last 5 minutes. This may indicate query pile-up, long-running queries, or insufficient resources.

## How to investigate
Check `system.processes` in ClickHouse for currently executing queries and identify any long-running or stuck queries.

